app="http://www.w3.org/2007/app">2012-06-05T12:46:25.584-04:00</app:edited><title>My Post @ The Good Men Project: "I Love It When You Call Me Big Poppa"</title><content type="html">&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;center&gt;&lt;h2 style="background-color: white; color: #333333; font-family: 'Bookman Old Style'; font-size: 24px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;"&gt;
&lt;a data-bitly-type="bitly_hover_card" href="http://goodmenproject.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/shutterstock_62751394.jpg" rel="lightbox[68823]" style="color: #444444; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, Verdana; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration: none;"&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-68826" height="347" src="http://goodmenproject.wpengine.netdna-cdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/shutterstock_62751394.jpg" style="border: none; display: block; margin: 50px auto 10px; max-width: 98%;" title="Photo by Shutterstock" width="583" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 style="background-color: white; color: #333333; font-family: 'Bookman Old Style'; font-size: 24px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0px 0px 5px; padding: 0px;"&gt;
&lt;em&gt;My wife and I had just received the best and most terrifying news of our lives – we were expecting a baby. I had just lost my job; how would I provide for my family as a struggling writer? Would I be able to be the father I wanted to be?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;a href="http://goodmenproject.com/ethics-values/i-love-it-when-you-call-me-big-poppa-a-black-writer-faces-fatherhood/"&gt;http://goodmenproject.com/ethics-values/i-love-it-when-you-call-me-big-poppa-a-black-writer-faces-fatherhood/&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;em&gt;***&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/center&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/center&gt;&lt;center&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;Blog Disclosure Policy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;Geoffrey Philp’s Blog Spot receives a percentage of the purchase price on anything you buy through links to Amazon, Shambala Books, Hay House, or any of the Google ads or Google Custom Search.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;center&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;***
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Disclaimer of Endorsement&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/center&gt;
