&lt;div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qThgrZ5KtK0/T7dOCZC-KuI/AAAAAAAAEJo/_vX1oSfvono/s1600/The_Matrix_Poster.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-qThgrZ5KtK0/T7dOCZC-KuI/AAAAAAAAEJo/_vX1oSfvono/s1600/The_Matrix_Poster.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;If Neo in &lt;i&gt;The Matrix 3&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;Had shot the Architect, he'd have been free.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;Then, he wouldn't have had to die,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;He'd have become RastafarI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;div style="text-align: center;"&gt;
&lt;span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
